为了可复用，我们要将一些常见的验证规则保存起来：

```js
const Rules = {
  longerThan6: val => val && val.length >= 6,
  isPhone: val => val && /(^1[3|5|8][0-9]{9}$)/.test(val),
  notEmpty: val => val && val.length != 0
};
```

要使用的时候:
```js
let {longerThan6, isPhone, notEmpty} = Rules;
```

